item.title: CVE-2013-4441|2024-08-06T16:45:14.717Z -- pwgen -- pwgen
item.description: The Phonemes mode in Pwgen 2.06 generates predictable passwords, which makes it easier for context-dependent attackers to guess the password via a brute-force attack.
